cycle PDCA Cycle

Plan | color: blue
  Define goals and processes
  -Execute plan-> | color: blue
Do | color: green
  Implement the plan
  -Evaluate results-> | color: green
Check | color: orange
  Measure and compare results
  -Improve process-> | color: orange
Act | color: red
  Adjust and standardize
  -Refine goals-> | color: red
